{"title":"Hexo的前置准备","uid":"f0c1ca3b0c9f9793ae5dde4fc58c7e46","slug":"Hexo个人博客搭建1","date":"2022-08-05T10:00:00.000Z","updated":"2022-08-05T18:57:25.401Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/Hexo个人博客搭建1.json","keywords":null,"cover":"/img/superh/1.jpg","content":"<p>Before use the Hexo to write down our articles , it was easy to see that something should be configured by ourselves.</p>\n<p>link:</p>\n<p>Hexo安装教程<a href=\"https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1Yb411a7ty\">https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1Yb411a7ty</a></p>\n<p>Aurora主题更换教程<a href=\"https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1hU4y1o7w3\">https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1hU4y1o7w3</a></p>\n<h2 id=\"一、-安装node-js\"><a href=\"#一、-安装node-js\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"一、 安装node.js\"></a>一、 安装node.js</h2><p>前往node.js官网<a href=\"https://node.js.org/\">https://node.js.org</a></p>\n<p>下载最新版本的安装包（<em>windows&#x2F;linux</em>）。选好解压位置，即可无脑下一步。</p>\n<p>打开cmd（管理员模式）输入以下代码查看<em><strong>node</strong></em>与<em><strong>npm</strong></em>版本，确认与所下版本一致。</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">node -v</code></pre>\n\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">npm -v</code></pre>\n\n<p>对<em>npm</em>换源以加快下载速度，选用淘宝的国内镜像：</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">npm install -g cnpm --registry&#x3D;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;registry.npm.taobao.org</code></pre>\n\n<p>查看<em>cnpm</em>下载情况</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">cnpm -v</code></pre>\n\n<p>等待下载完成，以后就可以直接使用<strong>cnpm</strong>进行包的安装。</p>\n<h2 id=\"二、-安装Git\"><a href=\"#二、-安装Git\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"二、 安装Git\"></a>二、 安装Git</h2><p>Git官网<a href=\"https://git-scm.com/\">https://git-scm.com/</a></p>\n<p>安装指南：<a href=\"https://blog.csdn.net/ACE_U_005A/article/details/122704934\">https://blog.csdn.net/ACE_U_005A/article/details/122704934</a></p>\n<p>安装视频(07)：<a href=\"https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1vy4y1s7k6\">https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1vy4y1s7k6</a></p>\n<h3 id=\"下面是个人安装历程\"><a href=\"#下面是个人安装历程\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"下面是个人安装历程\"></a><em><strong>下面是个人安装历程</strong></em></h3><details class=\"custom-details\">\n<summary>点击查看更多</summary>\n<p>1.官网下载安装包并解压（速度过慢建议使用迅雷下载）</p>\n<p>2.组件全✔</p>\n<p><img src=\"/source/img/photo/Git1.png\" alt=\"sample 截图\"></p>\n\n</details>\n<h2 id=\"三、-安装Hexo并配置\"><a href=\"#三、-安装Hexo并配置\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"三、 安装Hexo并配置\"></a>三、 安装Hexo并配置</h2><h2 id=\"四、-安装Aurora，配置主题\"><a href=\"#四、-安装Aurora，配置主题\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"四、 安装Aurora，配置主题\"></a>四、 安装Aurora，配置主题</h2><h2 id=\"五、-Github配置-x2F-初次上传网页\"><a href=\"#五、-Github配置-x2F-初次上传网页\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"五、 Github配置&#x2F;初次上传网页\"></a>五、 Github配置&#x2F;初次上传网页</h2><p>We mix the Github Pages and Hexo that is uisng the Aurora , which is a themes with powerful fuctions , to make up our personal Blog .</p>\n","feature":true,"text":"Before use the Hexo to write down our articles , it was easy to see that something should be configured by ourselves. link: Hexo安装教程https://...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":923,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"Blog","slug":"Blog","count":2,"path":"api/categories/Blog.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"Hexo","slug":"Hexo","count":2,"path":"api/tags/Hexo.json"},{"name":"Blog","slug":"Blog","count":3,"path":"api/tags/Blog.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E4%B8%80%E3%80%81-%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85node-js\"><span class=\"toc-text\">一、 安装node.js</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E4%BA%8C%E3%80%81-%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85Git\"><span class=\"toc-text\">二、 安装Git</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E4%B8%8B%E9%9D%A2%E6%98%AF%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%E5%8E%86%E7%A8%8B\"><span class=\"toc-text